          "description": "They look nice, and I like supporting a local pharmacy, but it is hard to get information about prescription pickups-- they are not always accurate. For example, today, they told me around 1pm that my prescription was ready, but when my wife went to pick it up, they didn't have it.\n\nI really can't recommend this pharmacy as a place to pick up prescriptions, but I hope they get better and figure things out. I think the main reason they struggle to communicate consistently is that they have to coordinate with another pharmacy, West Side Pharmacy, as this location is not able to directly take insurance.",
