          "description": "For many years, I had pretty good service from this pharmacy. Now that my insurance includes medicare, for prescriptions, they have told me that they do not phil.Medicare prescript. They use another pharmacy to show those prescriptions and that pharmacy is supposed to send the prescription over two them, and then they are supposed to deliver it. However, for my last three prescriptions, I have heard all kinds of stories about the delivery part. They just don't seem to dable to deliver my prescriptions. This last time I called three times and they said they were on their way. The last time they said it had been delivered and was outside my door, which of course it was not. Finally, I called them back and told them that it was not there, and all of a sudden, they found the drugs sitting in their own pharmacy. That has been the case each time. They lied to me every other time I called today. I'm done with this place.",
